# host-specific deployment config — replace with the equivalent for a new host if migrating
# Cloudflare Pages: place as `public/_redirects` (copied into dist) or project `_redirects`.
#
# Canonical hostname (update the left-hand host if the preview URL changes):
# https://YOUR-SITE.pages.dev/*  https://saeedzarrini.ir/:splat  301
#
# True 404 status for unmatched paths (order matters — more specific first):
/en/*    /en/404.html   404
/*       /404.html      404
